defaultOur firm view
default, based on legal advice,
default is that the growth duty cannot justify a failure to discharge the Commission’s statutory duties or its objectives (under 
defaultthe Equality Act 2006 and Equality Act 2010), or justify acting in a way that is incompatible with European Union law and/or the Human Rights Act 1998. 
default&#xa0;
